* 2016-06-14 Volodymyr M. Lisivka  <vlisivka@gmail.com> - 3.0.0
- Backward compatibility is broken.
- Modules are guarderd by import.sh, so check for __module__DEFINED is not necessary anymore.
- Support for built-in documentation is added to import.sh.
- Many fixes and rewrites in modules.

